 ubuntu x docker :

	\_ interactive ubuntu session using docker 

		 ~$ docker pull ubuntu 
		 ~$ docker run -it imageID
		 	#this gets you inside terminal
				~$ apt install php
				# above process installs php on ubuntu
			# restart container
			 # this wont be interactive
				~$ docker start Container_id
				~$
			# for interactive
				~$ docker exec -it container id /bin/bash
				#inside container (interactive)
				~$ exit
 
			# stop a container
			
				~$docker stop container_id		
